{"tid":2353253,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊：新加入律政司律師須學習內地法律　視野更清晰","createTime":"2021-01-04T14:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T02:32:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"eb02d96d7c80276a6228ad551ab1f97d2083eb90","tid":2353253,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T14:52:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568616-20210104.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568616-20210104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=f365f763\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568616-20210104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=086d9f7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568616-20210104.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊表示，律政司新增一個項目，新加入律政司的律師在首3年試用期間，必須學習內地法律的基礎原則4日，包括學習憲法、基本法、國安法等，可令他們的法律視野更清晰。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊在立法會司法及法律事務委員會的視像會議又說，本港作為國際法律樞紐及爭議解決服務中心，加上剛在大灣區落實的律師專業服務開放措施，香港需要培育更多法律專才，律政司將配合特區政府即將推出「大灣區青年就業計劃」，鼓勵企業聘請及派駐本地大學畢業生到大灣區內地城市工作。"},{"pid":"6c5618e6908457c036de16b6dac769d8bf8ec272","tid":2353253,"uid":274149,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"屌！pcll 就嚟無人讀"},{"pid":"4d5d702bf4241014f6c02186ec83a9808cdcae2f","tid":2353253,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6c5618e6908457c036de16b6dac769d8bf8ec272","tid":2353253,"uid":274149,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"屌！pcll 就嚟無人讀"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:07:07.000Z","msg":"清華大學開PCLL<br />\n<br />\n摺咗香港既 PCLL 咪得囉"},{"pid":"a58d0109cbdeec195719b0e37b269015df231a01","tid":2353253,"uid":44358,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:08:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">本港作為國際法律樞紐及爭議解決服務中心</span><br />\n<br />\n重發緊春